### 게시글 작성
POST {{domain}}/api/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My first post",
  "content": "This is my first post",
  "categoryId": 1
}

### 게시글 목록 조회
GET {{domain}}/api/posts?categoryId=1&page=1&limit=10

### 게시글 상세 조회
GET {{domain}}/api/posts/1

### 게시글 내용 수정
PATCH {{domain}}/api/posts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Update my content"
}

### 게시글 삭제
DELETE {{domain}}/api/posts/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}